  "3166810": {
    "name": "内幕交易 Insider Trading",
    "steam_appid": 3166810,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款<strong>以股市为主题的Roguelike牌组构建游戏</strong>，稍有不慎，你精心营造的市场就有可能彻底崩盘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/9d9e38e9e1266d585090c4931b8a377a.poster.avif?t=1772255660\" width=1100 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/9d9e38e9e1266d585090c4931b8a377a.webm?t=1772255660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/9d9e38e9e1266d585090c4931b8a377a.mp4?t=1772255660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《内幕交易》是一款以操纵股市为主题的牌组构建游戏。在每局游戏中，你将扮演一名拥有独特策略风格的交易员，带着一套能够影响市场走势的卡牌进入市场。打出手牌调整股价并控制市场波动。贪婪就像是驱动利益与风险的火箭燃料。只有你自己能够决定何时收手套现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/bca3841ecab1304e107fe8e24d9f7f91.poster.avif?t=1772255660\" width=1100 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/bca3841ecab1304e107fe8e24d9f7f91.webm?t=1772255660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/bca3841ecab1304e107fe8e24d9f7f91.mp4?t=1772255660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用卡牌，把市场玩坏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这并不是一款股市交易模拟游戏。这是一个由<strong>你的选择</strong>构成的牌组构建游戏。在休市期间，你可以前往盘后交易市场并在不同卡池中抽取手牌，但要小心，收益往往与风险并存。有些卡牌能够让牌组变得更强。有些则恰恰相反。开市之后，你只能够依赖精心构建的牌组来左右股价走势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/133e38666325edd12f2526498c9cda4b.poster.avif?t=1772255660\" width=1100 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/133e38666325edd12f2526498c9cda4b.webm?t=1772255660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/133e38666325edd12f2526498c9cda4b.mp4?t=1772255660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>风格各异的交易狂人</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一位可操纵角色都是身怀绝技的股票交易员，他们将以独一无二的方式来驾驭市场。你需要在游玩过程中逐步掌握他们的特殊之处。不同角色的初始牌组与特殊机制能够带来全新的可能性，这将鼓励你尝试不同寻常的策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/f121e64a61510df10eb98ef759ef5646.poster.avif?t=1772255660\" width=1100 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/f121e64a61510df10eb98ef759ef5646.webm?t=1772255660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/f121e64a61510df10eb98ef759ef5646.mp4?t=1772255660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精准胜过蛮干</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每一局游戏中，你都需要围绕“本周的财务目标”不断调整策略。过于冒进将会导致股价虚高难以买进。过于保守意味着只能眼睁睁看着机会溜走。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><br><strong>关键特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >120+卡牌供你拉升、抛售并从股价获利</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60+可堆叠的药丸与特性将带来意想不到的搭配</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各个可解锁角色将带来独特牌组与机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >连击系统将奖励你的巧妙布局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经济衰退等突发事件，随时打乱你的计划</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种难度设置，满足硬核挑战需求</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这真的是股市吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不。《内幕交易》是一款披着华尔街外衣的Roguelike牌组构建游戏。战胜市场、积累财富、气哭沃伦·巴菲特。最重要的是，你不用真的赔光存款。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/acfb2df3386b48f40473ae0a6e401854.poster.avif?t=1772255660\" width=1100 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/acfb2df3386b48f40473ae0a6e401854.webm?t=1772255660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166810/extras/acfb2df3386b48f40473ae0a6e401854.mp4?t=1772255660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
